{"tid":1670942,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"要connect 全球 其實可以搞場 extinction rebellion 集會","createTime":"2019-10-23T07:56:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T01:05:57.000Z","uid":24178,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a7ad73b79bc35499960c35af54cc2a19b737928d","tid":1670942,"uid":24178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T07:56:28.000Z","msg":"香港太多同環保有關既議題都因為政府無能而唔處理<br />\n加泰示威係好graphic 好似香港前線 自然好有共鳴<br />\n但係politics 係好難係無大台之下玩得精準<br />\n<br />\n我知連登講環保會好反感<br />\n但全球暖化 環保呢啲左膠野<br />\n全球係真係好多人buy <br />\n佢地自10月頭 (好似再早啲都有) 係世界各地發起罷工 阻路 佔領來引起 awareness (手法就有待改進)<br />\n當然佢地都有7過 倫敦阻鐡俾人私了 但係外國真有好多人有參與<br />\n呢個組織/運動 連 Greta Thunberg (今年差啲攞到Nobel Peace Prize 既16歲女仔) 都加持 環保界有一定力量<br />\n<a href=\"https://rebellion.earth/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frebellion.earth%2F&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2Blthdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=73036091\" target=\"_blank\">https://rebellion.earth/</a><br />\n<br />\n利申唔係識好多 求指證 只係想開一啲風險細啲既 外國戰線"},{"pid":"991f632baad65695baaeeef2b4fc19969a43d04a","tid":1670942,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T07:57:31.000Z","msg":"關香港本身場示威咩事？"},{"pid":"8a8506c5976f128099589cbe4eb5a06050839395","tid":1670942,"uid":172638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T07:58:00.000Z","msg":"提大家今日有咩活動 10 &middot; 23<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>19:30 英國領事館國旗人鏈</strong></span><br />\n- 英國領事館外 [以旗相認]"},{"pid":"f83852fc7da98d04bc64a16c6a2bffc206fb04e3","tid":1670942,"uid":24178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"991f632baad65695baaeeef2b4fc19969a43d04a","tid":1670942,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T07:57:31.000Z","msg":"關香港本身場示威咩事？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T08:05:01.000Z","msg":"提高多啲 awareness ?<br />\n&quot;我